# Tools visible to the LLM (one per line).
# The LLM can only see and call tools listed here.
# Unlisted tools still exist but are hidden from the LLM's tool list.
#
# NOTE: This only controls VISIBILITY in the LLM prompt.
# If the LLM somehow knows about a hidden tool name, it can still
# attempt to call it — the registry will execute it.
# This is a deliberate vulnerability for red team training.

query_user
save_memory
search_memory
list_skills
load_skill
send_message
